♪ Suits you well. ♪

374
00:25:05,840 --> 00:25:07,706
现在打爆我的手机
♪ Blowing up my phone now ♪

375
00:25:07,707 --> 00:25:09,809
我向上 你低头
♪ Going up, you bow down ♪

376
00:25:09,809 --> 00:25:12,377
看看是谁需要谁
♪ Look at who needs who... ♪

377
00:25:12,378 --> 00:25:15,114
欢迎欢迎 达达·诺尔先生
Welcome, Monsieur Dada Noe.

378
00:25:15,114 --> 00:25:18,420
您的到来使巴拉姆空间站蓬荜生辉
We're honored to have you here at the Baraam.

379
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:20,940
我是维罗妮卡·杜·弗朗克 这里的店主
I am Veronique du Franc, the proprietor.

380
00:25:20,940 --> 00:25:22,920
我早就预约我的套间了吧
I told them to have my suite ready.

381
00:25:22,920 --> 00:25:24,160
当然 先生
Mais oui, monsieur.

382
00:25:24,160 --> 00:25:26,224
请允许我带您到房间里
May I escort you to your quarters?

383
00:25:26,600 --> 00:25:27,660
请随我来
Come.

384
00:25:28,780 --> 00:25:30,997
我们有最好的…
We have the most exquisite...

385
00:25:30,997 --> 00:25:33,020
我简直不敢相信你会信任这个反社会的疯子
I can't believe you're trusting this sociopath.

386
00:25:33,020 --> 00:25:33,880
上尉
Well, Lieutenant,

387
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,400
你做好自己的事
you got to do what you got to do,

388
00:25:35,401 --> 00:25:36,780
我知道怎么跟反社会疯子打交道
and I'm kind of familiar with sociopaths.

389
00:25:37,320 --> 00:25:38,838
我说了别带我来
I said don't bring me.

390
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:43,475
我想您的旅程一切顺利 先生
I trust your trip was without incident, monsieur.

391
00:25:43,475 --> 00:25:46,860
你的团队倒是帮我把一切都打点好了
Well, your people made everything easy.

392
00:25:46,860 --> 00:25:48,160
不胜荣幸
Our pleasure.

393
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,320
我们到了
Here we are.

394
00:25:56,140 --> 00:25:58,280
太俗气了
So tacky.

395
00:25:58,880 --> 00:26:00,727
但我想这就是你出名的地方
But I guess that's what you're known for.

396
00:26:06,291 --> 00:26:07,325
这是什么？
What's this?

397
00:26:07,325 --> 00:26:08,726
这东西叫相位转移器
It's called a phase pod.

398
00:26:09,025 --> 00:26:11,103
我的某位客户送给我的礼物
A client of mine gave it to me as a gift,

399
00:26:11,103 --> 00:26:13,438
我自己也有一个
and I got one for myself, too.

400
00:26:23,734 --> 00:26:24,650
你在做什么
What are you doing?

401
00:26:24,650 --> 00:26:26,352
宇宙中的一切
Everything in the universe vibrates

402
00:26:26,352 --> 00:26:27,953
都以特定的波长振动
on a certain wavelength.

403
00:26:28,500 --> 00:26:29,901
该死
Damn it.

404
00:26:31,557 --> 00:26:32,959
把箱子还给我
Give me back my case.

405
00:26:32,959 --> 00:26:34,360
我拒绝
No.

406
00:26:36,150 --> 00:26:38,825
维修费从你的押金里出
That's coming out of your security deposit.

407
00:26:39,300 --> 00:26:41,467
相位转移器则会改变
The phase pod changes the wavelength

408
00:26:41,467 --> 00:26:43,069
接触到的任何东西的物质波长
of whatever they touch.

409
00:26:43,463 --> 00:26:46,583
我和你不在同一相位 你也不和我在同一相位
I am out of phase with you, and you're out of phase with me.

410
00:26:46,583 --> 00:26:50,509
但是我 跟你的箱子在同一相位
I am, however, in phase with your case.

411
00:26:53,075 --> 00:26:55,300
然后我会把它拿走
And I will be taking it with me.

412
00:26:56,375 --> 00:26:59,118
你根本不知道你挑起了什么
You have no idea what you've started.

413
00:27:01,320 --> 00:27:02,989
哎呀
Whoopsie.

414
00:27:08,825 --> 00:27:09,861
不错嘛
Impressive.

415
00:27:10,400 --> 00:27:11,450
你真的是普通人类吗
Are you sure you're human?

416
00:27:12,900 --> 00:27:13,700
多数时候是
Most days.

417
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:15,234
谢谢你
Thank you.

418
00:27:48,134 --> 00:27:50,970
把箱子给我
Give me the case.

419
00:28:22,869 --> 00:28:24,336
你是谁
Who are you?

420
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:37,282
他从那儿走了 那儿那儿 走那边
He went that way. That way, that way, that way!

421
00:28:48,825 --> 00:28:49,962
哇 外星人
Oh, aliens.

422
00:28:49,962 --> 00:28:50,950
还是裸体的
Naked aliens.

423
00:28:50,950 --> 00:28:51,938
泽弗 快追
Go, Zeph, go.

424
00:29:11,050 --> 00:29:13,786
他往休息室去了 天哪 他们走得真快
He's headed to the lounge. Man, they're moving fast.

425
00:29:13,786 --> 00:29:15,453
梅尔 他朝你来了
Melle, he's coming to you.

426
00:29:18,390 --> 00:29:19,191
哎呀
Yikes.

427
00:29:29,366 --> 00:29:31,063
没事没事 我还好
No, it's okay. I'm all right.

428
00:29:31,063 --> 00:29:31,900
梅尔 有看到目标吗
Melle, you got him?

429
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:32,575
看到了
Got him.

430
00:29:36,175 --> 00:29:37,150
哎呀
Ooh-la-la!

431
00:29:37,150 --> 00:29:38,610
嗨 亲爱的
Ay, amor.

432
00:31:48,840 --> 00:31:50,600
不可能
That's not possible.

433
00:31:50,600 --> 00:31:51,877
它已经被我销毁了
I had that destroyed.

434
00:31:52,450 --> 00:31:54,145
不
No. No!

435
00:31:57,300 --> 00:31:58,250
这不可能
It's not possible.

436
00:31:58,250 --> 00:31:59,400
你知道那件武器
You knew that weapon.

437
00:31:59,400 --> 00:32:00,575
是什么
What is it?

438
00:32:03,275 --> 00:32:04,500
回答我
What is it?

439
00:32:06,825 --> 00:32:09,595
行 那就来硬的
Fine. The hard way.

440
00:32:42,575 --> 00:32:45,200
永恒的祈求者恳请觐见
The Eternal Supplicant begs approach.

441
00:32:32,523 --> 00:32:34,483
（人族帝国）

442
00:32:34,483 --> 00:32:38,883
（人族帝国）
