443
00:32:42,575 --> 00:32:45,200
永恒的祈求者恳请觐见
The Eternal Supplicant begs approach.

444
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,765
准了
You have my permission.

445
00:32:54,275 --> 00:32:56,900
参见至高无上的女皇陛下
All hail Her Most Imperial Majesty,

446
00:32:56,900 --> 00:32:58,010
崇上国母
Mother of the Fatherland,

447
00:32:58,010 --> 00:32:59,575
- 瓦肯领主 - 你带来的是什么
- Overlord of Vulc... - What is it?

448
00:33:01,180 --> 00:33:03,082
它完成了 陛下
It is finished, Your Majesty.

449
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:08,034
我的工程师们在哪
Where are my engineers?

450
00:33:09,450 --> 00:33:13,692
他们 他们在完工后结束了自己的生命
They... they took their own lives upon completion.

451
00:33:18,630 --> 00:33:21,300
你在为谁流泪 桑
Who is the tear for, San?

452
00:33:23,502 --> 00:33:25,371
说
Speak.

453
00:33:25,850 --> 00:33:28,474
是为您 陛下
It is for you, Majesty.

454
00:33:29,341 --> 00:33:31,510
这都是
It is all...

455
00:33:33,645 --> 00:33:35,314
为了您
...for you.

456
00:33:44,256 --> 00:33:46,992
我再问你 桑
I asked you a question, San.

457
00:33:48,760 --> 00:33:50,462
你为何为我而哭
Why do you cry for me?

458
00:33:55,150 --> 00:33:56,175
看着我
Look at me.

459
00:34:00,050 --> 00:34:03,475
你还记得我们是谁吗
Do you remember who we were?

460
00:34:04,443 --> 00:34:06,745
在这一切之前
Before all this.

461
00:34:06,745 --> 00:34:09,580
好奇的男孩
The curious boy.

462
00:34:09,581 --> 00:34:12,351
天真的女孩
The innocent girl.

463
00:34:13,575 --> 00:34:15,800
我只记得我的失败 陛下
I only remember my failure, Majesty.

464
00:34:15,800 --> 00:34:18,657
别对我撒谎
Don't lie to me.

465
00:34:21,025 --> 00:34:26,931
为了活下去 我们付出了别人无法想象的代价
We were the only ones who could understand the cost to stay alive.

466
00:34:26,932 --> 00:34:29,768
我们是一个集体
We made a team.

467
00:34:29,768 --> 00:34:33,500
彼此依靠 不可分割
We needed each other, didn't we?

468
00:34:33,500 --> 00:34:39,310
记得那时我们是靠着什么话语 彼此支撑着活下来的吗
What did we say to carry each other through, to survive together?

469
00:34:39,311 --> 00:34:41,147
我们虽为两人
We are two...

470
00:34:42,914 --> 00:34:44,650
但为一体
But one.

471
00:34:44,650 --> 00:34:47,186
我们虽为两人 但为一体
We are two but one.

472
00:34:48,050 --> 00:34:49,455
如果我说
If I said then,

473
00:34:49,455 --> 00:34:50,956
「我们逃跑吧」
"Let's run away,

474
00:34:50,956 --> 00:34:52,950
「逃离这场竞争」
"let's flee this competition

475
00:34:52,950 --> 00:34:55,660
「以及把我们和人族联系在一起的一切」
and everything that binds us to Terra,"

476
00:34:55,661 --> 00:34:58,029
你会说什么呢
what would you have said?

477
00:35:01,200 --> 00:35:05,404
您问这个问题的时机 比您认为的更富意味
The timing of your question is more poetic than you know.

478
00:35:08,000 --> 00:35:10,369
我会答应您
I would have said yes.

479
00:35:17,716 --> 00:35:19,050
只会在当时
Then.

480
00:35:21,550 --> 00:35:22,850
那么现在呢
But now?

481
00:35:24,550 --> 00:35:29,550
您本可以在您的治下创造一些美好的东西
You could have made something beautiful with your reign.

482
00:35:29,550 --> 00:35:32,375
然而 您却选择了让人制造此物
Instead, you chose to build this.

483
00:35:32,375 --> 00:35:35,225
这意味着我熟知的那个天真女孩
That means that innocent girl I knew,

484
00:35:35,225 --> 00:35:37,569
她已经
she has been...

485
00:35:39,175 --> 00:35:40,450
死了
...murdered.

486
00:35:41,273 --> 00:35:42,608
怎么回事
What is this?

487
00:35:44,075 --> 00:35:45,543
你
You...

488
00:35:45,544 --> 00:35:48,380
你服用了一样的毒药?
You took the same poison?

489
00:35:50,015 --> 00:35:52,800
不 我不许你死
No! I forbid you to die!

490
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:56,275
没有人愿意活在
No one wants to live

491
00:35:56,275 --> 00:35:59,225
您的统治中 皇帝
in your world, Emperor.

492
00:35:59,225 --> 00:36:02,294
你就是个怪物
You are a monster!

493
00:36:29,875 --> 00:36:33,400
这是什么令人愉快的地方
And what delightful place is this?

494
00:36:33,400 --> 00:36:34,525
一个安全屋
A safe house.

495
00:36:34,525 --> 00:36:37,228
但对你而言也许不是
But maybe not so safe for you.

496
00:36:37,229 --> 00:36:39,175
既然你是31区的
You are Section 31.

497
00:36:39,175 --> 00:36:42,150
你为什么不拷问我以获取答案
Why aren't you torturing answers out of me?

498
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:43,850
你是个暴君
You're a tyrant.

499
00:36:43,850 --> 00:36:45,250
货真价实的
A real one.

500
00:36:45,250 --> 00:36:46,950
折磨起不到半点作用
Torture wouldn't work.

501
00:36:46,950 --> 00:36:49,940
你怎么会这么了解我这种人呢
How do you know so much about people like me?

502
00:36:51,443 --> 00:36:55,647
是在哪里学来的暴君手段 而且学得很到位
You learned tyranny somewhere, and you learned hard.

503
00:36:56,900 --> 00:36:59,017
藏着掖着 只证明了你的软弱
If you have to hide it, that's a weakness.

504
00:37:01,487 --> 00:37:04,088
而我 不能容许搭档有这种弱点
And I can't have that in a partner.

505
00:37:04,089 --> 00:37:05,425
我们可算不上搭档
We're not partners.

506
00:37:05,425 --> 00:37:06,575
不是吗
No?

507
00:37:06,575 --> 00:37:08,575
我可是帮了大忙了
I've been very helpful.

508
00:37:08,575 --> 00:37:10,500
你的计划行不通
You had a plan that couldn't work.

509
00:37:10,500 --> 00:37:11,575
而我给了你更好的
I gave you a better one.

510
00:37:11,575 --> 00:37:14,025
你让我尝到了那种刺激
You gave me a taste of the action,

511
00:37:14,025 --> 00:37:15,701
还明知道我会上瘾
knowing I'd want more.

512
00:37:17,336 --> 00:37:18,970
你需要我
You need me.

513
00:37:18,970 --> 00:37:21,206
你选择了我
You chose me.

514
00:37:23,274 --> 00:37:24,376
为什么呢
Why?

515
00:37:24,376 --> 00:37:26,800
不管你认为你的任务是什么
Whatever you believed your mission was,

516
00:37:26,800 --> 00:37:28,975
这远比你想象的更糟糕
it's worse than you thought.

517
00:37:28,975 --> 00:37:33,400
事关数亿万生命 时间紧迫
Billions of lives are at stake, and time is short.

518
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:37,188
你先让我了解你 我才能告诉你
Tell me you, and I will tell you me.

519
00:37:37,188 --> 00:37:41,250
要想合作 我得知根知底
The only way this works is if I know exactly

520
00:37:41,250 --> 00:37:43,350
说出你的身份
who I'm dealing with.

521
00:37:54,940 --> 00:37:57,250
我也不属于这个时代
I'm not from this time, either.

522
00:37:58,925 --> 00:38:01,250
我出生于20世纪的地球
I was born on Earth, 20th century.

523
00:38:01,250 --> 00:38:04,750
这么说你已经350岁高龄了
You are 350 years old?

524
00:38:04,750 --> 00:38:06,151
差不多
More or less.

525
00:38:06,151 --> 00:38:08,587
大部分时间我在冬眠舱里
I slept most of that time.

526
00:38:10,150 --> 00:38:11,557
在我被流放之后
After my exile.

527
00:38:14,360 --> 00:38:16,562
优生战争
The Eugenics Wars.

528
00:38:19,134 --> 00:38:22,868
强化人
Augments...

529
00:38:22,868 --> 00:38:24,470
夺走了我的星球
took my planet.

530
00:38:25,771 --> 00:38:27,773
我的家乡
My home.

531
00:38:33,144 --> 00:38:36,247
当时我们差不多有十个人在战斗
There was maybe ten of us who fought.

532
00:38:36,247 --> 00:38:39,718
我认识的人不是挨了一枪就是挨了一刀
Everyone I knew either took a bullet or a blade.

533
00:38:40,550 --> 00:38:42,685
我也还以颜色
But I gave some back.

534
00:38:44,063 --> 00:38:45,457
这让她注意到了我
She noticed me.

535
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:49,994
那个屠杀我家人的强化人
The Augment who slaughtered my family.

536
00:38:49,994 --> 00:38:55,066
他们叫她 被标记的吉里
They called her Giri the Marked.

537
00:38:55,066 --> 00:38:56,901
她收留了我
She took me in.

538
00:38:56,902 --> 00:39:00,300
让我比任何人类都强大
Made me stronger than any human should be.

539
00:39:00,300 --> 00:39:02,175
她把我撕成碎片
She ripped me apart

540
00:39:02,175 --> 00:39:05,242
然后把我重塑成了她军队里的又一个强化人
and turned me into another Augment for her army.

541
00:39:05,243 --> 00:39:08,600
我做了很多可怕的事
And I did terrible things.

542
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:12,751
却是为你这样的怪物效力
All for a monster like you.

543
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:18,550
因为对于暴君来说 永远只有一个选择
Because for tyrants, there is only one choice:

544
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,560
杀戮
murder.

545
00:39:22,861 --> 00:39:24,623
但你却没杀掉我
You haven't killed me.

546
00:39:26,323 --> 00:39:27,633
暂时而已
Yet.

547
00:39:33,550 --> 00:39:35,600
我之所以能认出那个武器
I recognized the weapon because

548
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:38,625
因为它是我下令造的
I ordered it to be built.

549
00:39:41,175 --> 00:39:42,850
召集你的人手
Gather your people.

550
00:39:42,850 --> 00:39:45,150
每个人都得派上用场
We're gonna need every one of them.

551
00:39:59,403 --> 00:40:00,643
（加密传讯2）

552
00:40:00,643 --> 00:40:05,103
（加密传讯2）
（天赐之物）

553
00:40:22,100 --> 00:40:23,700
在我的宇宙里
In my universe,

554
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:25,300
阴谋重重 政敌环伺
there were always plotters.

555
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:26,763
政变层出不穷
Always a coup.

556
00:40:26,763 --> 00:40:30,075
所以我造了一件武器来终结所有威胁
So I built a weapon to end all threats.

557
00:40:30,975 --> 00:40:33,000
我称之为
I called it

558
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,350
「天赐之物」
the Godsend.

559
00:40:35,375 --> 00:40:37,300
它会引发一种连锁反应
It triggers a chain reaction,

560
00:40:37,300 --> 00:40:39,825
就像病毒一样在群星间传播
like a virus passing between planets.

561
00:40:39,825 --> 00:40:42,306
所到之处 一切都将化为灰烬
Everything in its path incinerates.

562
00:40:42,307 --> 00:40:45,250
整个象限都会消失
An entire quadrant would be lost.

563
00:40:45,250 --> 00:40:47,700
如果我的敌人成功杀死了我
If my enemies managed to kill me,

564
00:40:47,700 --> 00:40:50,448
那也不会有东西留给他统治
there would be nothing left to rule.

565
00:40:53,250 --> 00:40:55,025
有个小问题
Yeah, hi. Quick question.

566
00:40:55,025 --> 00:40:55,587
不好意思
Sorry.

567
00:40:55,587 --> 00:40:57,825
就一个很小很小的问题
Yeah, no. Uh, just a qu-- it's just a quick one.

568
00:40:57,825 --> 00:41:01,259
这是天赐之物还是天赐之暮
Is it Godsend or God's End?

569
00:41:02,425 --> 00:41:03,600
天赐之物还是天赐之暮
Godsend or God's End?

570
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:05,050
我不明白你说的有什么区别
I don't hear a difference in what you're saying.

571
00:41:05,050 --> 00:41:08,475
听不出来吗 「物」和「暮」
Really? Really? Godsend. God's End.

572
00:41:08,475 --> 00:41:09,375
我还是没听明白
Yeah, I'm still not getting it.

573
00:41:09,375 --> 00:41:10,375
天赐之物是...
The Godsend is...

574
00:41:10,375 --> 00:41:12,200
噢 天赐之物 我现在听清楚了
Wait, Godsend. I hear it now.

575
00:41:12,200 --> 00:41:13,975
-天赐之物 不是暮 -物
- It's Godsend. No apostrophe. - Send.

576
00:41:13,975 --> 00:41:15,541
天赐之物就在这个宇宙
The Godsend is here.

577
00:41:15,541 --> 00:41:18,100
怎么会 那可是另一个宇宙的物品
How? It's from another universe.

578
00:41:18,100 --> 00:41:19,850
我不知道 但那个人刚刚就拿着它
I don't know, but that man had it.

579
00:41:19,850 --> 00:41:21,600
你以为是达达·诺伊的那个人
The one that you think is Dada Noe.

580
00:41:22,125 --> 00:41:23,625
我们都知道是达达·诺伊的那个人
The one we know is Dada Noe.

581
00:41:23,625 --> 00:41:26,800
不 他不可能是你们的达达·诺伊 
No, he's not your Dada Noe. He can't be.

582
00:41:26,800 --> 00:41:28,225
他来自人族帝国
He's from the Terran Empire,

583
00:41:28,225 --> 00:41:29,725
是他把天赐之物带来这里
and he brought the Godsend here.

584
00:41:29,725 --> 00:41:32,575
不然他根本不可能知道那到底是什么
That's the only way he can know about it.

585
00:41:32,575 --> 00:41:34,425
既然我们已经抓到他了
And since we have him locked up tight,

586
00:41:34,425 --> 00:41:35,800
我要亲自审讯他
I'll interrogate him.

587
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,875
绝对不行 不能信这个女人说的话
No, no, no. We cannot trust a single word this woman says.

588
00:41:37,875 --> 00:41:38,600
是啊
Yeah.

589
00:41:38,600 --> 00:41:40,050
她害死了梅尔
She cost us Melle.

590
00:41:40,050 --> 00:41:42,100
只有她知道我们面对的是什么人
She's the only one who knows what we're dealing with.

591
00:41:42,100 --> 00:41:43,975
也就是她自己说的 小兄弟
Yeah, well, so she says, little bro.

592
00:41:43,975 --> 00:41:44,650
小?
Little?

593
00:41:45,550 --> 00:41:47,175
这是身材羞辱
Scale-shamer!

594
00:41:47,175 --> 00:41:48,975
微生物比恐龙更长寿
Microbes outlasted dinosaurs!

595
00:41:48,975 --> 00:41:50,700
冷静点 我要说的是
Calm your boots. What I'm saying is...

596
00:41:50,700 --> 00:41:53,711
我要尿在你的装甲上 直到你全身生锈
I will piss in your suit until you go all rusty like!

597
00:41:53,712 --> 00:41:55,400
这一切都是她搞砸的
...that she's the reason this is all bollixed up.

598
00:41:55,400 --> 00:41:56,725
她导致了梅尔的死
She's the reason Melle's dead, 

599
00:41:56,725 --> 00:41:58,875
她也是我们被派来这的原因
and she's the reason we're in the ass end of the galaxy.

600
00:41:58,875 --> 00:42:00,018
听好了
Listen up.

601
00:42:03,050 --> 00:42:05,175
乔久和我回船上去
Georgiou and I are gonna go back to the ship.

602
00:42:05,175 --> 00:42:07,600
达达·诺伊是我们与天赐之物的唯一联系
Dada Noe is our only link to the Godsend,

603
00:42:08,226 --> 00:42:11,329
所以我们要找他谈谈
so we're gonna have a little chat with him.

604
00:42:23,842 --> 00:42:25,143
干什么
What?

605
00:42:25,143 --> 00:42:27,077
她叫菲利帕·乔久
Her name is Philippa Georgiou,

606
00:42:27,078 --> 00:42:29,125
至高无上的女皇陛下
Her Most Imperial Majesty.

607
00:42:29,125 --> 00:42:30,748
崇上国母
Mother of the Fatherland.

608
00:42:30,749 --> 00:42:32,250
瓦肯领主
Overlord of Vulcan.

609
00:42:32,250 --> 00:42:34,750
克罗诺斯征服者 安多利女王
Dominus of Qo'noS, Regina Andor,

610
00:42:34,750 --> 00:42:38,088
菲利帕·乔久·奥古斯都·伊波尼亚斯·塞塔瑞斯
Philippa Georgiou Augustus Iaponius Centarius.

611
00:42:38,549 --> 00:42:39,650
酷
Cool.

612
00:42:39,650 --> 00:42:40,700
配薯条的吗
That come with fries?

613
00:42:42,150 --> 00:42:43,152
很好笑 对吧
That was good, right?

614
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,625
好吧
Okay.

615
00:42:46,625 --> 00:42:49,133
每次你不直接回答她的问题
Every time you don't answer her questions directly,

616
00:42:49,134 --> 00:42:52,270
女皇陛下就会狠狠地打你的脸
Her Majesty will punch you in your face.

617
00:42:52,270 --> 00:42:53,225
好吧
Fine.

618
00:42:55,050 --> 00:42:56,500
我是达达
I'm Dada.

619
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:58,800
达达·诺伊 先念达达 再是诺伊
Dada Noe. Just Dada, then Noe.

620
00:42:58,800 --> 00:42:59,950
就是这样 没有中间
That's it. No in-betweens.

621
00:43:00,275 --> 00:43:02,112
然后 我
And I, uh...

622
00:43:02,113 --> 00:43:06,517
我以前在瓦特殖民地开过一家病理学实验室
I used to run a pathology lab in the Watt Colonies.

623
00:43:12,290 --> 00:43:13,791
搞什么鬼
What the shit, man?!

624
00:43:13,792 --> 00:43:17,028
你明明说揍我脸的会是她
You said that she was gonna be doing the face punching!

625
00:43:17,028 --> 00:43:20,431
现在我俩都说谎了 你不是那个达达
So now we both have lied. You are not that Dada.

626
00:43:21,600 --> 00:43:23,868
你是那些人口中说的他的镜像版本
You're what these people call his Mirror.

627
00:43:25,675 --> 00:43:28,350
你来自人族帝国
You came here from the Terran Empire,

628
00:43:28,350 --> 00:43:30,700
而且还带来了天赐之物
and you brought the Godsend.

629
00:43:30,700 --> 00:43:32,210
什么天赐之物
What's the Godsend?

630
00:43:33,611 --> 00:43:36,250
我自己的军事委员会曾想要废黜我
My own war council tried to depose me.

631
00:43:36,250 --> 00:43:39,250
你知道我是怎么说服元帅开口的吗
Do you know how I convinced the field marshal to talk?

632
00:43:48,193 --> 00:43:49,427
我曾是个管理员
I was an administrator

633
00:43:49,427 --> 00:43:51,450
在帝国里的武器设施工作
at an Imperial weapons facility on Terra.

634
00:43:52,350 --> 00:43:53,000
没错
Uh, yeah.

635
00:43:53,000 --> 00:43:56,234
天赐之物被存放在我管理的设施中
The Godsend was stored at my facility.

636
00:43:57,600 --> 00:43:59,700
大多数人认为这只是一个传说
Most thought it was a legend,

637
00:43:59,700 --> 00:44:01,550
但我知道这是真的
but I knew it was real.

638
00:44:01,550 --> 00:44:03,025
所以你想卖掉它
So you tried to sell it.

639
00:44:03,025 --> 00:44:04,174
是 是的
Yeah, yeah.

640
00:44:04,175 --> 00:44:07,913
我想靠得来的收益安静地生活在这里
I wanted to live here quietly on its proceeds.

641
00:44:07,913 --> 00:44:09,580
你是怎么来到我们的宇宙的
How did you get to our universe?

642
00:44:13,885 --> 00:44:15,653
当时发生了一场离子风暴
There was an ion storm.

643
00:44:15,653 --> 00:44:17,275
实际上是两场
Two of them, actually.

644
00:44:17,275 --> 00:44:20,550
它们像对好了表一样准时相遇
And when they converged, which they do like clockwork,

645
00:44:20,550 --> 00:44:23,750
撕裂了帝国边界某处的时空
they ripped something open on the fringes of the Empire--

646
00:44:23,750 --> 00:44:25,550
他们称之为异象
an anomaly, they called it--

647
00:44:25,550 --> 00:44:28,375
但这实际上是一条通道
but it was a passageway

648
00:44:28,375 --> 00:44:31,136
从人族帝国通往这里
to get to this place from the Terran Empire.

649
00:44:32,625 --> 00:44:36,550
从你们宇宙的新月星云穿出
Comes out through your Crescent Nebula.

650
00:44:36,550 --> 00:44:38,900
至少目前还是鲜有人知的
Few know about it. For now.

651
00:44:38,900 --> 00:44:41,479
但它四小时后会重新开放
But it'll open again in four hours.

652
00:44:41,479 --> 00:44:44,025
那本来是我要去见买家的时间
That's when I was supposed to be meeting my buyer.

653
00:44:44,450 --> 00:44:46,500
你知道那武器的威力吗
Are you aware of what that weapon does?

654
00:44:46,500 --> 00:44:48,850
人族帝国已经耗尽了所有资源
The Terran Empire's burned through its resources.

655
00:44:48,850 --> 00:44:50,325
饥荒肆虐 饿殍遍地
There's famine.

656
00:44:50,325 --> 00:44:52,825
整个生态系统正在崩溃
Entire ecologies are collapsing.

657
00:44:52,825 --> 00:44:54,925
它们需要寻找新的领土
They need to find a new territory

658
00:44:54,926 --> 00:44:57,050
进行征服和压榨
to conquer and strip-mine.

659
00:44:57,050 --> 00:44:59,229
当他们意识到他们的超级武器不见了
When they realize that their superweapon is gone,

660
00:44:59,230 --> 00:45:01,275
他们一定会找到那条通道
they're gonna find that passageway--

661
00:45:01,275 --> 00:45:02,975
你知道他们会的 然后来到这里
you know they will-- and they'll come

662
00:45:02,975 --> 00:45:06,304
烧杀抢掠每一寸领土 再奴役余生
and they'll burn everything they touch and enslave the rest,

663
00:45:06,304 --> 00:45:09,925
您的帝国向来如此 陛下
because that's what the Empire does, Majesty.

664
00:45:10,825 --> 00:45:12,625
他们学您学到了精髓
They learned well from you.

665
00:45:14,875 --> 00:45:16,446
还有谁想要它？
Who else wants it?

666
00:45:16,447 --> 00:45:18,925
我真的不知道
I-I don't know, man.

667
00:45:18,925 --> 00:45:21,225
我收到了一个报价 钱是真的
I got an offer. The money was real.

668
00:45:21,225 --> 00:45:23,525
有人偷走了我们的天赐之物
Someone stole the Godsend from us.

669
00:45:23,525 --> 00:45:24,500
究竟是谁
Who was he?

670
00:45:24,500 --> 00:45:25,650
我真不清楚
No idea.

671
00:45:25,650 --> 00:45:29,175
无论是谁闯入我的套间 偷走了那件武器
Whoever broke into my room, whoever stole that weapon,

672
00:45:29,175 --> 00:45:30,175
知道这些事的人
they know what they know 

673
00:45:30,175 --> 00:45:31,950
肯定是从你们其中之一得来的
because they learned it from one of you.

674
00:45:51,616 --> 00:45:54,452
紧急传送
Emergency transporter.

675
00:46:29,254 --> 00:46:30,200
这下好了
Well, this is great.

676
00:46:31,400 --> 00:46:33,150
更棒了
Oh, even better.

677
00:46:33,150 --> 00:46:35,175
那是我们的船吗 船炸了吗
Is that... is that the ship? Is the ship gone?

678
00:46:35,175 --> 00:46:36,475
我还挺喜欢那艘船的
I liked that ship.

679
00:46:36,475 --> 00:46:37,675
什么情况
What happened?

680
00:46:38,350 --> 00:46:39,931
有人搞破坏
Sabotage.

681
00:46:43,300 --> 00:46:44,534
什么
What?

682
00:46:44,535 --> 00:46:47,105
偷走天赐之物的人有一个同伙
Whoever stole the Godsend had a partner.

683
00:46:47,105 --> 00:46:48,975
就在我们几个之中
It was someone here.

684
00:46:51,042 --> 00:46:53,625
这意味着我们中的一个是内鬼
Which means one of us is a mole.

685
00:47:00,250 --> 00:47:01,050
可能是你
Could be you.

686
00:47:01,050 --> 00:47:01,950
原话奉还
Could be you.

687
00:47:02,600 --> 00:47:05,825
要是我的话 我早把你们都杀了
If it were me, I would have murdered all of you already.

688
00:47:05,825 --> 00:47:07,550
大哥 你是了解我的
Look, boss, if there's a mole,

689
00:47:07,550 --> 00:47:08,350
绝对不可能是我
you know it's not me.

690
00:47:08,350 --> 00:47:10,725
虽然这话听起来也就很像内奸说的 我也不确定
I mean, that sounds pretty moley to me. I don't know.

691
00:47:11,525 --> 00:47:13,100
我们合作过差不多十次了
We've been on like ten ops together.

692
00:47:13,100 --> 00:47:15,350
是没错 但我连你长什么样都不知道
Yeah, and I still don't even know what you look like, do I?

693
00:47:15,350 --> 00:47:16,935
没人知道查莫人长什么样子
No one knows what a Chameloid looks like.

694
00:47:16,935 --> 00:47:18,750
你可以变成任何你想变的样子
You might change into anything you want.

695
00:47:18,750 --> 00:47:19,905
那法兹呢
What about Fuzz, huh?

696
00:47:19,905 --> 00:47:21,850
他的体型与其他人都不在一个尺度上
He exists on a whole other scale than anybody else.

697
00:47:21,850 --> 00:47:22,575
转移话题是吗
Mm, deflecting?

698
00:47:22,575 --> 00:47:25,850
我的妻子即将产下我们的第一窝卵囊
My wife is about to lay our first litter of egg sacs.

699
00:47:25,850 --> 00:47:29,275
而且我还有19万只幼崽正在路上
No, I have 190,000 hatchlings on the way...

700
00:47:29,275 --> 00:47:30,550
- 我希望他们活下去  - 那你听着
- and I want them to live.  - Well, look,

701
00:47:30,550 --> 00:47:32,075
你可以在我们中的任何人找到动机
you could find a motive for any of us.

702
00:47:32,075 --> 00:47:34,375
也可能是你们中任何两个的组合
Or it could be a combination of any of you.

703
00:47:34,375 --> 00:47:36,250
你看 就像泽弗和法兹或者其他
You know, like-like Zeph and-and Fuzz or...

704
00:47:36,250 --> 00:47:38,550
你还漏掉了梅尔
You are spinning out without Melle.

705
00:47:38,550 --> 00:47:39,850
你根本没法做出判断
You cannot land on a choice.

706
00:47:39,850 --> 00:47:41,350
也许是你想给我灌输这个观点
Maybe you're putting that in my head

707
00:47:41,350 --> 00:47:42,200
因为你才是内鬼
because you're the mole.

708
00:47:42,200 --> 00:47:43,700
又会不会是加勒特 她可是新来的
Huh? How about Garrett? She's new.

709
00:47:43,700 --> 00:47:44,875
她才不在乎我们
She doesn't care about us.

710
00:47:45,375 --> 00:47:46,375
我可是星际舰队的军官
I'm Starfleet.

711
00:47:47,525 --> 00:47:50,400
还有没有人像我一样感受到一阵英雄主义的风
Anyone else feel that heroic breeze right there

712
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:51,302
弄乱了她的斗篷?
ruffling her cape?

713
00:47:51,302 --> 00:47:53,875
听我讲 那边有一艘旧船
Okay, there's an old ship out there,

714
00:47:53,875 --> 00:47:55,075
一艘旧垃圾驳船
an old garbage scow.

715
00:47:55,075 --> 00:47:56,641
我发现它的时候你们还在
Yeah, I found it when you were up there

716
00:47:56,641 --> 00:47:58,242
审问那个金属脑袋
interrogating metal head.

717
00:47:59,200 --> 00:48:00,575
肯定已经很多年没人驾驶过它了
Must be years since anyone flew it,

718
00:48:00,575 --> 00:48:01,437
但我认为我们可以修复它
but I think we can work with it

719
00:48:01,450 --> 00:48:03,915
开着它去追捕拿走天赐之物的人
to go after whoever took the Godsend.

720
00:48:04,900 --> 00:48:06,283
我没那么讨厌你了
I dislike you less.

721
00:48:07,785 --> 00:48:09,575
如果我想有人喜欢我 我就会养一只狗
If I wanted someone to like me, I'd get a dog.

722
00:48:10,192 --> 00:48:11,325
我喜欢秩序
I like order.

723
00:48:11,325 --> 00:48:13,024
我喜欢预测和结论
I like prediction and conclusion.

724
00:48:13,400 --> 00:48:14,750
那你可来错队伍了
Then you're on the wrong team

725
00:48:14,750 --> 00:48:16,100
因为我们这还没揪出内鬼
because we've got mole,

726
00:48:17,362 --> 00:48:19,530
被困在一颗荒无人烟的星球
stranded on a dead planet,

727
00:48:19,530 --> 00:48:21,232
无法联络外界
no communication with the outside,

728
00:48:21,232 --> 00:48:25,136
而且不到四个小时之后人族将得到天赐之物
and less than four hours before the Terrans get the Godsend

729
00:48:25,136 --> 00:48:27,005
并在银河系的任意一处使用它
and use it anywhere in the galaxy.

730
00:48:27,775 --> 00:48:28,900
说起来
Speaking of which,

731
00:48:28,900 --> 00:48:31,075
小夸 天线阵列怎么样了
Quas, what about the antenna array?

732
00:48:31,075 --> 00:48:34,175
