You wouldn't bet on a horse named Pretty Certain.

752
00:49:27,139 --> 00:49:31,139
小夸、法兹 你们马上和乔久一起去船
Quas, Fuzz, you get to the scow right away with Georgiou.

753
00:49:31,139 --> 00:49:32,760
