and then 25%...

763
00:49:47,900 --> 00:49:49,580
别贫嘴了小夸 快出发
Quas, just get your ass out there.

764
00:49:49,580 --> 00:49:50,360
我也爱你 头儿
I love you, too, Cap.

765
00:49:50,360 --> 00:49:50,899
行了行了
All righty.

766
00:49:50,899 --> 00:49:51,438
遵命
Aye, aye.

767
00:50:03,260 --> 00:50:05,260
这艘旧船上的内部电路
The internal circuitry on this old scow

768
