Everything I'm seeing should work.

770
00:50:14,879 --> 00:50:17,600
所以我们正在追的东西 天赐之物
So this thing we're chasing, the Godsend,

771
00:50:18,200 --> 00:50:21,200
你的工程师 他们安装保险没有?
your engineers, did they install a fail-safe?

772
00:50:21,200 --> 00:50:23,121
