Can we disable it remotely?

773
00:50:25,400 --> 00:50:26,880
没有这种保险
There is no fail-safe.

774
00:50:26,880 --> 00:50:28,493
我不会允许的
I wouldn't allow it.

775
00:50:28,493 --> 00:50:30,960
不愧是你
How very on-brand for you.

776
00:50:30,960 --> 00:50:32,259
可以再问你一个问题吗
Can I ask you one more question?

