And you didn't answer my question.

787
00:50:57,980 --> 00:50:59,857
渐进线圈不见了
The asymptote coil is gone.

788
00:51:01,459 --> 00:51:04,339
肯定是有人为了铽元素把它拆走了
Someone must have scavenged it for the terbium.

789
00:51:04,339 --> 00:51:06,800
那再找一个 这个东西应该能飞
Well, find another one, this thing should fly.

790
00:51:07,420 --> 00:51:08,640
也许货舱就有
Maybe the cargo hull.

791
00:51:09,220 --> 00:51:10,440
别去
Huh. Oh, no, no.

792
00:51:10,440 --> 00:51:12,419
每个人都待在一起 好吗
Everyone stays together, all right?

793
00:51:12,899 --> 00:51:15,273
降低你杀死我们的可能性
Limits the possibilities of you killing us.

794
00:51:17,840 --> 00:51:19,109
我们去货舱吧
Let's go to the cargo hold, please.

795
00:51:19,110 --> 00:51:20,911
你不来吗
Aren't you coming?

796
00:51:21,459 --> 00:51:23,881
当然 我可太高兴了
Yes. I couldn't be more excited.

797
00:51:27,240 --> 00:51:29,254
当然 我可以下去帮你
Yeah, I could help you down there, of course,

798
00:51:29,254 --> 00:51:31,522
但考虑到 控制我们的行动
but considering how, you know, control

799
00:51:31,522 --> 00:51:33,779
是你整个身份的核心
is central to your entire identity

800
00:51:33,779 --> 00:51:35,526
而我本来就不太能接受这种事
and the fact that I'm just not good at it,

801
00:51:36,080 --> 00:51:37,680
所以我就站在这里 
I'm just gonna stand here 

802
00:51:37,680 --> 00:51:40,464
- 为了我们的关系 什么也不做了 - 那你还真热心呢
- and honor our relationship by doing absolutely nothing. - Helpful.

803
00:51:40,465 --> 00:51:42,166
这叫做彻底的自我接纳
It's called radical self-acceptance.

804
00:51:42,480 --> 00:51:43,960
- 那你真是进步了 - 谢谢夸奖
- Evolved of you. - Well, thank you.

805
00:51:43,960 --> 00:51:45,236
所以说 你能修好它吗？
So, can you fix it?

806
00:51:45,760 --> 00:51:47,720
我甚至不确定它是否坏了
I'm not even sure it's broken.

807
00:51:47,720 --> 00:51:49,307
它只是缺了个零件
It's just missing a part.

808
00:51:49,600 --> 00:51:51,508
看这里 这些被乱扯的线路看着很严重
Look, this-this torn wiring looks dramatic,

809
00:51:51,509 --> 00:51:53,800
