but this equipment has redundancy built in.

810
00:51:53,800 --> 00:51:55,000
有一个简单的解决办法
There's an easy work-around.

811
00:51:55,000 --> 00:51:58,515
唯一问题是 有人取出了θ节点
Except somebody ripped out the theta junction.

812
00:51:58,516 --> 00:52:00,760
除此之外 这个东西应该可以用
Other than that, this thing should work.

813
00:52:00,760 --> 00:52:03,388
好吧 也许我们的内鬼拿走了它
Okay, well, maybe our mole has it.

814
00:52:08,259 --> 00:52:09,400
加勒特?
Garrett?

815
00:52:09,400 --> 00:52:10,280
咋了
Yeah.

816
00:52:10,880 --> 00:52:11,980
泽弗
Zeph.

817
00:52:11,980 --> 00:52:13,180
泽弗去哪了
Where is Zeph?

818
00:52:21,272 --> 00:52:22,940
泽弗 收到请回复
Zeph, come in.

819
00:52:24,175 --> 00:52:26,411
泽弗 你能听到吗
Zeph, do you copy?

820
00:52:33,751 --> 00:52:35,100
泽弗
Zeph.

821
00:52:43,760 --> 00:52:44,862
加勒特 是你做的吗
Garrett, was that you?

822
00:52:48,880 --> 00:52:50,501
加勒特 刚刚那是什么情况
Garrett, what the hell was that?

823
00:52:50,501 --> 00:52:52,259
有人刚激活了天线阵列
Someone just activated the antenna array.

824
