加勒特 情况简报
Garrett, sitrep.

827
00:52:59,980 --> 00:53:01,712
越来越棒了
This is going to be good.

828
00:53:01,712 --> 00:53:04,582
上尉 收到请回复 完毕
Lieutenant, do you copy? Over.

829
00:53:13,280 --> 00:53:14,019
安全
Clear.

830
00:53:15,180 --> 00:53:15,920
安全
Clear.

831
00:53:16,620 --> 00:53:17,894
这里什么都没有
Nothing here.

832
00:53:17,895 --> 00:53:20,220
怎么会有人用这个来发出信号呢
How could someone have used this to send out a signal?

833
