不可能 它少了一个部件
Impossible. It's missing a part.

834
00:53:23,400 --> 00:53:25,299
有人把它打成了筛子
And someone shot it to hell.

835
00:53:25,299 --> 00:53:26,360
我听到有人在跑
I heard someone running.

836
00:53:27,000 --> 00:53:28,899
泽弗一定是把θ节点放回去了
Zeph must have put the theta junction back in.

837
00:53:29,219 --> 00:53:30,960
使用完毕后 射击毁掉了阵列
Then shot it after he used the array.

838
00:53:34,739 --> 00:53:37,180
所以他肯定是在擅离职守后绕回来的
So he must have circled back after he went AWOL.

839
00:53:37,740 --> 00:53:40,700
泽弗来这个星球来阻碍我们
Zeph came down to this planet to sabotage us.

840
00:53:41,852 --> 00:53:43,621
现在我们被困住了
And now that we're stranded,

841
00:53:43,621 --> 00:53:46,499
他用阵列给同谋发了信息
he sent a message to whoever he's working with.

842
00:53:46,499 --> 00:53:48,158
他会潜伏直到撤离的船抵达
And he'll lay low until his ride gets here,

843
00:53:48,158 --> 00:53:50,240
然后溜之大吉
and then he's long gone.

844
00:53:50,240 --> 00:53:51,920
那我们得先找到他
Then we need to find him first.

845
00:54:00,860 --> 00:54:02,460
观察者 能收到吗
Observer, do you copy?

846
00:54:02,460 --> 00:54:04,808
拜托 突袭者一号 我什么时候收不到了
Please, Raider One, when do I not copy?

847
