就在这个区域 完毕
was just in this sector. Over.

851
00:54:15,620 --> 00:54:18,723
收到 保持低调 保持队形
Copy. Stay low and tight, people.

852
00:54:22,760 --> 00:54:24,800
你曾效力的那个军阀 吉里
The warlord you served, Giri,

853
00:54:24,800 --> 00:54:25,740
她后来怎样了
what happened to her?

854
00:54:26,507 --> 00:54:27,980
她死了 死于生前最爱的事
She died like she lived.

855
00:54:27,980 --> 00:54:29,867
你知道我说的什么
By that, you know what I mean.

856
00:54:30,860 --> 00:54:31,640
她很幸运
She was lucky.

857
00:54:31,640 --> 00:54:33,480
没染上良心这种东西
She wasn't infected with a conscience.

858
00:54:33,480 --> 00:54:34,380
染上?
Infected?

