00:56:36,739 --> 00:56:37,699
当然
Sure.

899
00:56:37,699 --> 00:56:40,280
只是这段视频很可能和他一起被谋杀了
Except the footage was probably murdered along with him.

900
00:56:40,280 --> 00:56:42,920
我们可以将三录仪连接到外骨骼装甲上
We could connect one of the tricorders to his suit.

901
00:56:43,240 --> 00:56:44,499
就算没剩多少数据
Whatever data is left,

902
00:56:44,499 --> 00:56:45,900
凶手也昭然若揭了
we'll know who did this.

903
00:56:45,900 --> 00:56:48,720
说得好像我们都是嫌疑人一样
You say that like we're all suspects.

904
00:56:48,720 --> 00:56:50,419
并不是 好吗
We're not. All right?

905
00:56:50,419 --> 00:56:53,820
那时候我 法兹和乔久都在那艘船里
Fuzz, me and her were in the scow when all this happened--

906
00:56:53,820 --> 00:56:55,880
每个人都在彼此的视线范围内
everyone in sight of everyone else.

907
00:56:55,880 --> 00:56:58,415
没一个人乱跑 没错吧
And nobody went anywhere, right?

