916
00:57:38,300 --> 00:57:39,539
<i>检测到血液</i>

917
00:57:41,219 --> 00:57:42,400
呃 那不可能啊
Well, that's impossible.

918
00:58:00,180 --> 00:58:01,779
加勒特上尉
Lieutenant Garrett,

919
00:57:55,723 --> 00:57:57,102
<i>痕迹匹配</i>

920
00:58:01,779 --> 00:58:04,649
为什么你的指甲缝里会有泽弗的血
why is Zeph's blood underneath your fingernails?

921
00:58:09,840 --> 00:58:11,280
加勒特上尉
Lieutenant Garrett,

922
00:58:11,280 --> 00:58:14,620
在泽弗的尸体上发现了你的证据
evidence from you was found on Zeph's body,

923
00:58:14,620 --> 00:58:17,560
泽弗尸体上的证据也在你身上发现了
and evidence from Zeph's body was found on you.

924
00:58:18,240 --> 00:58:19,880
不像星际舰队的作风啊
Not very Starfleet.

925
00:58:19,880 --> 00:58:21,431
我问心无愧
Oh, I am very Starfleet.

926
00:58:22,060 --> 00:58:23,640
你清楚凶手并不是我
And you know I didn't do this.

927
00:58:24,720 --> 00:58:27,605
你只是害怕任何有道德准则的人
You are just terrified of anyone with a moral compass.

928
00:58:29,006 --> 00:58:32,843
但在那颗纯洁的小心灵的深处
And deep down in that pure little heart,

929
00:58:33,779 --> 00:58:36,540
你其实是个混乱小妖精 没错吧
you're actually a chaos goblin, aren't you?

930
00:58:36,540 --> 00:58:38,620
- 我知道你是这样的 小天使  - 别这么叫我
- I know you have it in you, angel. - Don't call me that.

931
00:58:38,620 --> 00:58:40,620
星际舰队发现了这样的你
Starfleet sniffed you out

932
00:58:40,620 --> 00:58:43,379
把你放在了最能发挥你作用的地方
and put you in a place where you'd be most useful.

933
00:58:43,379 --> 00:58:46,320
31区正是为那些打破规则
Section 31 is just the place for officers 

934
00:58:46,320 --> 00:58:50,920
却又从未真正越界的军官准备的地方
who bend the rules, never quite break them until they do.

935
00:58:50,920 --> 00:58:54,464
而你 正好适合这里
And you fit right in here.

936
00:58:59,820 --> 00:59:01,280
你想怎么折磨我都可以
You can torture me all you want.

937
00:59:01,280 --> 00:59:03,708
但我坚持自己没杀过人
You will never make me a murderer.

938
00:59:05,175 --> 00:59:06,220
住手
No.

939
00:59:21,059 --> 00:59:22,627
我们拿到录像了
We've got footage!

940
00:59:26,380 --> 00:59:27,180
住手
Stop!

941
00:59:27,539 --> 00:59:28,833
快住手
Stop!

942
00:59:30,768 --> 00:59:32,339
这是我的装甲
This is my suit.

943
00:59:32,339 --> 00:59:34,504
我即是装甲！
I am the suit!

944
00:59:35,606 --> 00:59:37,974
装甲就是我！
The suit is me!

945
00:59:37,975 --> 00:59:39,509
等一下
One second.

946
00:59:43,013 --> 00:59:44,700
我们是你的朋友
We were your friends.

947
00:59:45,459 --> 00:59:46,720
曾是你的朋友
We were your friends.

948
00:59:47,619 --> 00:59:49,452
你杀不了我
You can't kill me.

949
00:59:49,453 --> 00:59:50,220
泽弗 别
Zeph, no.

950
00:59:50,220 --> 00:59:51,280
你不能
You can't kill...

951
00:59:57,360 --> 00:59:59,080
泽弗是自杀的?
Zeph killed himself?

952
00:59:59,720 --> 01:00:00,831
他为什么要这么做
Why would he do that?

953
01:00:02,400 --> 01:00:05,720
抱歉让您失望了 陛下
Sorry to disappoint you, Your Majesty.

954
01:00:07,360 --> 01:00:09,459
这一切根本说不通
Look, none of this is making any sense.

955
01:00:09,459 --> 01:00:10,819
是啊 非常之不合理
No, none of it makes a lick of sense.

956
01:00:10,819 --> 01:00:12,259
他为什么要这样做呢
Why would he do this?

957
01:00:12,760 --> 01:00:13,980
给我几分钟时间
Give me a couple minutes to...

958
01:00:13,980 --> 01:00:14,920
我们没时间了
We don't have minutes.

959
01:00:14,920 --> 01:00:16,881
那就几秒钟行了没
Well, then give me a couple seconds, then.

960
01:00:19,760 --> 01:00:20,640
可能是你
Could be you.

961
01:00:20,640 --> 01:00:21,420
原话奉还
Could be you.

962
01:00:21,420 --> 01:00:22,920
但我连你长什么样都不知道
And I still don't even know what you look like.

963
01:00:22,920 --> 01:00:24,880
你可以变成任何你想变的样子
You could change into anything you want.

964
01:00:24,880 --> 01:00:26,419
她是新来的 她才不在乎我们
She's new. She doesn't care about us.

965
01:00:26,419 --> 01:00:27,360
我可是星际舰队的军官
I'm Starfleet.

966
01:00:28,060 --> 01:00:29,939
当你在说我这套装甲的时候
When you are talking about the suit,

967
01:00:30,448 --> 01:00:32,040
就是在说我
you're talking about Zeph.

968
01:00:32,040 --> 01:00:33,219
这可不是法兹
This isn't Fuzz.

969
01:00:33,219 --> 01:00:34,998
这个瓦肯外表不过是台机器
The Vulcan's just a machine, you know.

970
01:00:34,999 --> 01:00:36,532
我在里面呢
I'm inside.

971
01:00:36,533 --> 01:00:38,200
这是身材羞辱
Scale-shamer!

972
01:00:38,200 --> 01:00:41,180
你绝对想不到我能进入多小的地方
You wouldn't believe the tiny spots I can get into.

973
01:00:41,180 --> 01:00:45,875
比如 身体改造组件的内部空间
For example, the inner workings of body modifications.

974
01:00:45,876 --> 01:00:47,699
当时他启用了自动驾驶
There's an autopilot.

975
01:00:47,699 --> 01:00:49,980
这是唯一合理的解释
That's the only thing that makes sense.

976
01:00:51,800 --> 01:00:55,953
你给瓦肯机器设定了自动驾驶程序
You set the Vulcan machine on autopilot.

977
01:00:57,454 --> 01:01:01,190
所以当时它的反应才那么古怪
That's why its responses were so strange.

978
01:01:02,040 --> 01:01:02,960
你来不来
Aren't you coming?

979
01:01:03,420 --> 01:01:04,340
当然
Yes.

980
01:01:06,140 --> 01:01:09,198
你钻进了泽弗的外骨骼装甲
You flew into Zeph's exoskeleton.

981
01:01:09,840 --> 01:01:11,560
你钻进去之后
And once you were inside...

982
01:01:11,560 --> 01:01:13,500
有人把西塔接口拆掉了
Somebody ripped out  the theta junction.

983
01:01:13,500 --> 01:01:14,960
加勒特 泽弗去哪了
Garrett, where's Zeph?

984
01:01:16,774 --> 01:01:19,360
然后你控制了泽弗的装甲
Then you took control of Zeph's suit.

985
01:01:21,080 --> 01:01:23,360
当别人在找他的时候
While the others were out looking for him,

986
01:01:23,360 --> 01:01:25,581
你控制他溜回了通讯阵列
you made him sneak back into the antenna array

987
01:01:25,582 --> 01:01:27,219
然后发送了那些信息
and send those messages.

988
01:01:28,259 --> 01:01:30,019
不要这么做
Don't do this to them!

989
01:01:30,620 --> 01:01:32,300
我们是你的朋友啊
We were your friends.

990
01:01:32,300 --> 01:01:35,091
然后你销毁了所有证据
Then you destroyed the evidence.

991
01:01:35,400 --> 01:01:36,626
还杀掉了泽弗
And you killed Zeph.

992
01:01:38,840 --> 01:01:40,760
然后你再把这一切嫁祸给加勒特
And then you planted the evidence on Garrett here.

993
01:01:45,745 --> 01:01:47,280
举起手来 法兹
Hands up, Fuzz.

994
01:01:47,280 --> 01:01:49,840
真是倒了血霉了
Oh, shite and ever shite.

995
01:01:57,180 --> 01:01:59,980
阿洛克 你不会真的要信她的鬼话吧
You're honestly gonna believe what she says, Alok?

996
01:01:59,980 --> 01:02:02,160
夸西 我们一起经历了这么多 你也信她的话吗
Quasi, after everything we've been through?

997
01:02:04,721 --> 01:02:07,391
我能先说一句吗
C-Can I just say one thing first?

998
01:02:12,520 --> 01:02:14,264
泽弗的外骨骼我还控制着呢
I'm still hacked into Zeph's exoskeleton.

999
01:02:27,978 --> 01:02:28,979
喂
Come on!

1000
01:02:33,820 --> 01:02:36,053
说好的「不抛弃任何人」呢
What happened to "no crew member left behind"?

1001
01:02:53,640 --> 01:02:55,080
快一点啊
Come on, come on!

1002
01:02:55,080 --> 01:02:56,106
靠近他们
Get us closer.

1003
01:04:07,219 --> 01:04:09,280
接住你了
I got you. I got you.

1004
01:04:09,280 --> 01:04:10,600
还好有我
Nice and easy.

1005
01:04:10,600 --> 01:04:11,459
该死
Damn.

1006
01:05:10,274 --> 01:05:12,920
你很关注黑市的动向 没错吧
You keep tabs on the black market, hmm?

1007
01:05:12,920 --> 01:05:14,720
你就是在那听说天赐之物的消息的
And that's where you heard about the Godsend.

1008
01:05:14,720 --> 01:05:16,080
你在乎这些干什么
Why do you care?

1009
01:05:16,080 --> 01:05:17,847
家人你都下得去手
You killed your family.

1010
01:05:17,847 --> 01:05:19,516
再多点人算什么呢
What's a few billion more people, huh?

1011
01:05:20,259 --> 01:05:22,739
天赐之物在哪 你的同谋是谁
Where is it? And who are you working with?

1012
01:05:22,739 --> 01:05:24,120
你登上了皇位
You took your crown

1013
01:05:24,120 --> 01:05:27,424
他们却痛苦地死在你的脚边
while they died in agony not ten feet away.

1014
01:05:28,520 --> 01:05:31,840
你奴役了你唯一的朋友
You condemned your only friend to slavery,

1015
01:05:31,840 --> 01:05:35,164
居然还有脸在最后一刻给他一些怜悯?
and then you had the balls to offer him kindness at the end?

1016
01:05:37,440 --> 01:05:39,236
你怎么会知道的
How could you know that?

1017
01:05:39,720 --> 01:05:41,740
你终于发现了
Glad you're catching on.

1018
01:05:41,740 --> 01:05:44,008
他把你耍了 女皇陛下
He played you, Emperor.

1019
01:05:44,400 --> 01:05:46,043
桑还活着
San's alive.

1020
01:05:50,880 --> 01:05:53,183
不可能
It's not possible.

1021
01:05:55,440 --> 01:05:56,739
绝对不可能 到底怎么回事
That's not possible. How?

1022
01:05:56,739 --> 01:05:59,556
他训练出了对毒药的抗药性
He built up an immunity from that poison, you know.

1023
01:05:59,556 --> 01:06:02,726
每次只多服用很小的剂量
Teeny tiny doses over time.

1024
01:06:03,994 --> 01:06:07,779
看样子是小混蛋又赢了一次
Once again, small shite for the win, mama.

1025
01:06:08,739 --> 01:06:10,620
他在哪
Where is he?!

1026
01:06:11,020 --> 01:06:12,819
期待他的精彩表演吧
He's gonna put on quite the show.

1027
01:06:13,600 --> 01:06:15,379
你制造了天赐之物
You built the Godsend.

1028
01:06:15,379 --> 01:06:17,299
你制造了一个怪物
You made this monster.

1029
01:06:17,299 --> 01:06:19,209
全是因为你
This is all you.

1030
01:07:03,219 --> 01:07:05,387
小心点可以吗
Be careful, all right?

1031
01:07:06,040 --> 01:07:08,040
我让你小心点
I said be careful.

1032
01:07:08,040 --> 01:07:10,019
我还得用它活动呢
I have to get around in that.

1033
01:07:13,672 --> 01:07:15,465
你都能买得起一百多具身体了 还在乎这一具
You can afford a hundred of them now.

1034
01:07:15,465 --> 01:07:16,666
太好了
Oh, great.

1035
01:07:17,360 --> 01:07:19,320
这个能用不就行了
I'd settle for one that works.

1036
01:07:21,139 --> 01:07:23,000
所以就是这个
So that's it?

1037
01:07:23,000 --> 01:07:24,520
无敌的天赐之物
The almighty Godsend.

1038
01:07:24,520 --> 01:07:26,000
等你做上皇帝了
When you're emperor,

1039
01:07:26,000 --> 01:07:29,640
能不能给它换个没那么奇怪的名字
maybe start by naming it something less confusing.

1040
01:07:34,923 --> 01:07:37,822
<i>离子风暴会聚倒计时</i>

1041
01:07:43,539 --> 01:07:45,128
跨越两个宇宙的通道打开时
Once that passageway opens up,

1042
01:07:45,129 --> 01:07:48,200
他会联系人族 他们会从中进入
he contacts the Terrans, they come through.

1043
01:07:50,760 --> 01:07:52,301
然后他们会在此引爆
They're detonating it here.

1044
01:07:52,880 --> 01:07:55,580
他就会成为帝国的新宠
And he'd be the darling of the Empire.

1045
01:07:55,580 --> 01:07:58,339
发生这样的灾难 星联就会陷入混乱
So he throws the Federation into chaos...

1046
01:07:58,339 --> 01:08:00,419
星际舰队自顾不暇
Starfleet will start scrambling.

1047
01:08:00,419 --> 01:08:01,978
入侵的完美时机
Perfect time to invade.

1048
01:08:05,260 --> 01:08:06,540
你创造了它
You gave birth to this thing.

1049
01:08:08,600 --> 01:08:10,040
我们要如何阻止
How do we stop it?

1050
01:08:10,040 --> 01:08:11,100
没办法
We don't.

1051
01:08:11,100 --> 01:08:13,539
我们被困在这 追不上他
We're trapped here, so we can't follow him.

1052
01:08:13,539 --> 01:08:15,720
通讯天线坏了 我们也无法警告任何人
The antenna's destroyed, so we can't warn anybody.

1053
01:08:15,720 --> 01:08:17,026
胡扯
That is bullshit.

1054
01:08:18,540 --> 01:08:19,459
你肯定有更好的办法
You can do better than that.

1055
01:08:19,459 --> 01:08:20,230
我做不到
I can't.

1056
01:08:20,600 --> 01:08:21,660
天赐之物就像我自己
The Godsend is me.

1057
01:08:21,660 --> 01:08:23,640
我唯一无法战胜的就是自己
I'm the only one I could never defeat.

1058
01:08:27,400 --> 01:08:29,373
过去总是缠着你不放
The past always catches up with you.

1059
01:08:30,040 --> 01:08:30,819
不是吗
Right?

1060
01:08:35,100 --> 01:08:36,880
但并不意味着它总能赢
Doesn't mean it always wins.

1061
01:08:39,840 --> 01:08:41,985
每个安全屋都有备用计划
Every safe house, I have a backup plan.

1062
01:08:41,985 --> 01:08:43,440
把那艘垃圾船修好
We'll get that scow running.

1063
01:08:43,880 --> 01:08:46,856
老大 那家伙飞不起来的
Boss, the scow won't fly.

1064
01:08:47,240 --> 01:08:48,700
没有渐进线圈就不可能
Not without an asymptote coil.

1065
01:08:50,600 --> 01:08:52,296
我们有一个
We have one.

1066
01:08:52,296 --> 01:08:54,198
我们必须追上桑
We'll catch up with San.

1067
01:08:54,198 --> 01:08:55,740
我们要阻止他联系人族帝国
We'll make sure he can't contact the Terrans.

1068
01:08:56,880 --> 01:08:58,202
你早把线圈拆出来了
You ripped out the coil.

1069
01:08:58,202 --> 01:09:00,570
有内奸在 我可没法什么都说出来
Couldn't tell you while a mole was still running around.

1070
01:09:03,573 --> 01:09:05,409
你个混蛋
Asshole.

1071
01:09:18,021 --> 01:09:20,457
小夸 去帮她一下
Okay, Quas, give her a rip.

1072
01:09:26,280 --> 01:09:27,481
还是只有一下反应
Still just one pulse.

1073
01:09:33,520 --> 01:09:34,538
来活了 朋友们
And we're in business.

1074
01:09:34,538 --> 01:09:38,220
我们只有不到三十分钟时间
Okay, team, we have less than 30 minutes.

1075
01:09:38,220 --> 01:09:40,160
小夸 设定航线前往新月星云
Quas, set a course for the Crescent Nebula.

1076
01:09:40,160 --> 01:09:42,760
路上将会非常颠簸
All right, this is gonna be bumpy and bad.

1077
01:09:42,760 --> 01:09:44,800
我推测桑的星舰会有武器
I'm assuming San's ship will be armed.

1078
01:09:44,800 --> 01:09:46,640
废话 人族帝国能有不武装的星舰吗
Yeah, every Terran ship's armed.

1079
01:09:47,080 --> 01:09:50,040
对方有质子加农炮 鱼雷
He'll have proton cannons, torpedoes,

1080
01:09:50,040 --> 01:09:52,656
而我们只有一堆垃圾
and we are a garbage barge.

1081
01:09:53,420 --> 01:09:54,324
有啥好笑的
Why are you laughing?

1082
01:09:54,324 --> 01:09:56,460
因为我想不出来还有什么更糟的情况了
Because I can't imagine things getting much worse.

1083
01:10:02,560 --> 01:10:03,399
出发
Let's go.

1084
01:10:13,760 --> 01:10:16,078
所以 这艘船会在自身周围制造牵引力场
So, this thing flies around in the middle of a tractor field.

1085
01:10:16,079 --> 01:10:18,280
人们向太空里面扔垃圾
People jettison their garbage into space,

1086
01:10:18,280 --> 01:10:20,360
然后这种驳船会拖着垃圾和力场
and the scow flies around and drags the trash

1087
01:10:20,360 --> 01:10:21,380
一起飞行
along with the field.

1088
01:10:22,319 --> 01:10:24,400
牵引力场里塞满垃圾之后
Once the tractor field is full,

1089
01:10:24,400 --> 01:10:26,220
就会一起把垃圾甩进星云里
it dumps the trash in the Nebula

1090
01:10:26,220 --> 01:10:28,000
让垃圾在辐射里自行分解
where it disintegrates in the radiation.

1091
01:10:29,000 --> 01:10:29,920
我就是想确认一下
I just want to be clear.

1092
01:10:29,920 --> 01:10:32,020
你是说我们最有可能用的上的武器
You're saying that our best potential weapon is

1093
01:10:32,020 --> 01:10:33,620
是用来拖垃圾的牵引光束吗
a beam for collecting garbage?

1094
01:10:33,620 --> 01:10:34,420
没错
Yes.

1095
01:10:34,420 --> 01:10:35,020
那太棒了
Great.

1096
01:10:35,020 --> 01:10:37,567
提醒下 你在那指手画脚帮不上一点忙
Hey, being judgy never helped anything.

1097
01:10:39,720 --> 01:10:40,620
你要去哪
Where are you going?

1098
01:10:40,620 --> 01:10:41,520
轮机室
Engineering.

1099
01:10:41,540 --> 01:10:43,000
如果那是我们唯一的武器
If that's our only weapon,

1100
